In this paper, two crypto-systems are presented. These crypto-systems are constructed on discrete logarithm problem Diffie-Hellmal-Pohlig crypto-system is based on Diffie-Hellman key predistribution procedure and Pohlig-Hellman crypto-system. Diffie-Hellman-ElGamal crypto-system is based on Diffie-Hellman key predistribution procedure and ElGamal crypto-system.